org.ektorp.support.GenericRepository<DefaultStorage<T>>
public class DatabaseRepository<T extends java.lang.Comparable>
extends org.ektorp.support.CouchDbRepositorySupport<DefaultStorage<T>>

The Class DatabaseRepository contains the methods to connect to the couchdb database and store and retrieve data from it.

It contains the standard methods of a CouchDbRepository (i.e. add, contains, remove and update) and defines more methods to retrieve data from the database.

Parameters:
class1 - the type defines the default type for the standard methods.
db - the db is used to connect to the couchdb database and perform the queries.
deviceID - the deviceID is stored to retrieve the documents containing data for the specified device.
